::KitKat::

She was getting things organized in her head. She was drumming up a 
plan on some things.

Destructor was in charge of his group and her Strategic General
Starscream was her General of War, 
Drillbit would be made captian of the ship. He'd be incharge of the 
other bots that were here. He would also be in charge of security.

She smiled, it was a plan. She liked it. With them dealing with most 
of the details, she could focus on other things.
